ThingShape.description: Standard Thing Shape for VFFS Model 3002 System using the property names needed for CogniPro (G. Kirkpatrick)
ThingShape.documentationContent:
10/20 - JEN removed the upper-case versions of 

param_CenterSealTempPV
param_DailyPackCounter
param_MachineSpeed
param_PumpInvSpeed
param_TotalPackCount
recipe_CenterSealTemperature
recipe_ChannelNumber
recipe_FitmentSealTemperature

that are replaced by the lower-case versions, which were what the team had to use to make the front-end work.

10/29 - GLEN adapted all Friendly Named in "Description" Field
